Q1

Pollution_Map = function(arg1) {
  pr = qnorm(1 - arg1, mean = mean(PSI), sd = sd(PSI));
  
  map <- ggplot() + geom_polygon(data = Popn.TWN.f, aes(x = long, y = lat, group = group), fill = "white", color = "black") + geom_point(data = EPA.STN@data, aes(x = EPA.STN@coords[,1], y = EPA.STN@coords[,2]), color = ifelse(EPA.STN@data$PSI > pr, "red", "blue")) + theme(text = element_text(family = "BiauKai")) + ggtitle("台灣空氣測站分佈") + coord_fixed(1.0);
  box <- ggplot(data = subset(EPA.STN@data, PSI > pr & SiteType != "背景測站"), aes(x = SiteType, y = PSI)) + geom_boxplot() + theme(text = element_text(family = "BiauKai"));
  multiplot(map, box, col = 1);
  
  return(pr);
}
Pollution_Map(0.3);

## [1] 68.21853
Pollution_Map(0.5);

## [1] 59.0274

2-2 大台北人口老化地圖

NORTH.TWN <- subset(Popn.TWN, COUNTY == "臺北市" | COUNTY == "新北市" | COUNTY == "基隆市" | COUNTY == "桃園市" | COUNTY == "宜蘭縣");
NORTH.TWN$RANK <- rank(-NORTH.TWN$AGING);

NTWN.LongLat <- spTransform(NORTH.TWN, CRS("+proj=longlat +datum=WGS84 +no_defs +ellps=WGS84 +towgs84=0,0,0")) #projection transfrom TWD97 -> WGS84
ul <- as.vector(cbind(bbox(NTWN.LongLat)[2,2], bbox(NTWN.LongLat)[1,1])) # lat-long coord
lr <- as.vector(cbind(bbox(NTWN.LongLat)[2,1], bbox(NTWN.LongLat)[1,2])) # lat-long coord

MyMap <- openmap(ul,lr, 9, "esri-topo");
plot(MyMap);
plot(spTransform(NORTH.TWN, osm()), add = TRUE, col = ifelse(NORTH.TWN$RANK < nrow(NORTH.TWN) * 0.2, rgb(1, 0, 0, alpha = 0.6), rgb(1, 1, 1, alpha = 0)));
title("Top 20% Aging Townships of Northern Taiwan")
